00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,490
=Episode 4=

4
00:01:08,490 --> 00:01:11,320
(Bamboo Dew Spring)

5
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:12,640
Then do you know

6
00:01:13,320 --> 00:01:14,600
who I am?

7
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:17,600
Of course I do.

8
00:01:19,720 --> 00:01:22,200
Nangong Xuanyu.

9
00:01:29,880 --> 00:01:32,360
Nangong Xuanyu is the most

10
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,400
powerful

11
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,800
and formidable man in the world.

12
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:37,320
Oh, yes.

13
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:39,640
You treated me to wine today.

14
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:41,840
I'll treat you next time.

15
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,760
We'll drink

16
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:44,840
flower wine.

17
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,480
Flower wine?

18
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:47,760
Mm.

19
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:52,080
Whatever flower you like,

20
00:01:52,480 --> 00:01:54,840
I'll brew wine from it for you.

21
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,760
Magnolia.

22
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:18,400
Magnolia.

23
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:21,840
Your Ladyship.

24
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:23,440
Ahead is the wine cellar.

25
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,320
Don't leave me behind.

26
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,800
I'll teach you another lesson.

27
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:34,000
A wise man stays away from danger.

28
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,520
Jerk.

29
00:02:55,660 --> 00:02:56,920
Didn't you say someone was here?

30
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:57,640
Where is he?

31
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,160
Your Majesty.

32
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:06,040
You said touching her

33
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:08,480
eases the burning pain inside you.

34
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,720
Then why not keep her as a living cure?

35
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,000
That would only worsen the problem.

36
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,360
How did she find out my identity?

37
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,640
Go investigate it thoroughly.

38
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,840
Yes.

39
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,960
I entered the palace

40
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:31,440
to marry the greatest man

41
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,720
and claim the highest power.

42
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,640
(Shen Zhinian.)

43
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,720
(If you want power,)

44
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:42,190
(that depends on
whether you have the fate for it.)

45
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:45,160
(That wine was way too strong.)

46
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:47,120
(My head hurts so much.)

47
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:49,320
(What exactly happened last night?)

48
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,720
(Why did I sleep inside a wine vat?)

49
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,360
(Find a eunuch's outfit
for me to change into.)

50
00:03:54,370 --> 00:03:56,120
(I should be able to return
to Tinglan Palace without being noticed.)

51
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:58,280
Young Master,
there's an injured sparrow over there.

52
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:05,620
(Jiang Chen,
eldest legitimate son of Duke Zhen)

53
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:06,800
Let's go.

54
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,400
We'll be late for court.

55
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,240
Take it back and nurse it well.

56
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:34,160
This young eunuch has a hangover

57
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,320
and caught a chill as well.

58
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:37,200
I'll prescribe him
some medicine shortly.

59
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,200
Thank you, my lord.

60
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,640
Please, my lord, you mustn't.

61
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:45,760
It's alright.

62
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,080
Which palace do you serve in?

63
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,840
I'll have someone deliver the medicine

64
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:51,480
to you later.

65
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,590
There's no need
to trouble yourself, my lord.

66
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,040
I'll come collect it myself.

67
00:04:56,080 --> 00:04:57,040
You're quite fortunate.

68
00:04:57,160 --> 00:04:58,080
Everyone knows

69
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,280
Lord Jiang of the Duke's Manor

70
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,880
has a truly kind heart.

71
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,400
You shouldn't refuse.

72
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:05,440
Lord Jiang.

73
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,720
(So he's Jiang Chen,
the Duke's eldest son.)

74
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,510
If you're worried about being punished,

75
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,440
I'll escort you back.

76
00:05:12,450 --> 00:05:14,760
That way your mistress
won't make things difficult for you.

77
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,160
Thank you, my lord.

78
00:05:22,100 --> 00:05:23,800
Senior Attendant,
you've finally returned.

79
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,360
What did she call you?

80
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,160
My surname is Chang.

81
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,920
They all call me Eunuch Chang.

82
00:05:32,280 --> 00:05:32,920
Eunuch Chang.

83
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,320
Thank you.

84
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:46,360
Miss, forget about Lord Jiang for now.

85
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,920
Last night, Fengqi Palace sent word

86
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,800
that you were
to pay respects to the Empress

87
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,120
this morning at chen hour.

88
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:51,840
Chen hour?

89
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,480
It's already a quarter past chen hour.

90
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,640
Why didn't you tell me sooner?

91
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:55,080
Quick.

92
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,050
Prepare the bath and dressing.

93
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:59,020
(Fengqi Palace)

94
00:06:09,520 --> 00:06:10,880
Greetings, Your Ladyship.

95
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,160
Lady Liu.

96
00:06:12,600 --> 00:06:13,440
Shen Zhinian.

97
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:16,000
I thought you'd built your own kingdom

98
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,680
and stopped showing up to court.

99
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,200
I would never dare.

100
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,520
I...

101
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:25,080
I merely caught a chill.

102
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,280
Last night, I already sent word.

103
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,800
If you couldn't come,
why didn't you report it earlier?

104
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:32,000
On my way here, I became dizzy

105
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,920
and fell.

106
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:35,080
My clothes were stained with dirt,

107
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:36,440
so I went back to change.

108
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:37,430
That's why I arrived late.

109
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:39,920
The Empress has arrived.

110
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,440
Greetings, Your Majesty.

111
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:51,420
(Empress Jiang Jin,
eldest legitimate daughter of Duke Zhen)

112
00:06:59,640 --> 00:07:00,560
Be seated.

113
00:07:00,570 --> 00:07:02,580
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

114
00:07:10,280 --> 00:07:11,840
Senior Attendant Rou is still unwell.

115
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:12,960
You may rise.

116
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,760
Thank you, Your Majesty.

117
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,400
Your Ladyship oversees the six palaces.

118
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:26,160
You've worked hard.

119
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:28,540
His Majesty's
birthday banquet is approaching.

120
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:29,960
How are the preparations?

121
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,400
Everything has been prepared.

122
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,760
Please review them, Your Majesty.

123
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:39,920
I'm only worried that
Your Majesty's health is too delicate

124
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,320
to read through so many pages.

125
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,200
All of you may leave.

126
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,340
Senior Attendant Rou stays behind.

127
00:07:58,080 --> 00:07:58,880
Help me

128
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,280
read through this register.

129
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:05,520
Yes.

130
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:17,920
Your Ladyship has quite the temper.

131
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:21,040
Sit for a while before leaving,
lest she makes things difficult for you.

132
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

133
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,720
Your Ladyship said

134
00:08:28,730 --> 00:08:31,490
since Senior Attendant Rou is so eager
to ease Her Majesty's burdens,

135
00:08:31,500 --> 00:08:33,460
you are to uproot every flower
in Shanglin Garden

136
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,400
and replace them all

137
00:08:34,400 --> 00:08:35,960
with the peonies Her Majesty favors.

138
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,600
If you fail to finish before sunset,

139
00:08:37,610 --> 00:08:39,380
you will be punished
according to palace rules.

140
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,680
Lord Jiang has arrived.

141
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:55,680
Your Majesty.

142
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:59,360
The foreign envoys have all
been settled at Wenhua Inn.

143
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:02,440
I came to ask whether Your Majesty
wishes to receive them.

144
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,520
You were late today.

145
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:08,720
I came across a sick young eunuch
in Shanglin Garden

146
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:10,380
and took him
to the Imperial Medical Bureau.

147
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,290
That's what delayed me.

148
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,400
In this world,

149
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,120
kindness

150
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:17,000
doesn't always get rewarded.

151
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:19,160
Since you've chosen to help others,

152
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:21,240
there's no need to expect gratitude.

153
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:25,840
Your Majesty.

154
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,320
Duke Zhen requests an audience.

155
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,160
I'll take my leave first.

156
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,320
Otherwise Father will nag at me again.

157
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:50,200
Greets, Your Majesty.

158
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:52,040
Rise, Duke.

159
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:57,100
(Duke Zhen)

160
00:09:58,110 --> 00:10:00,440
Wan Ning entered the palace today
to accompany the Empress.

161
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,160
Your Majesty watched Wan Ning grow up.

162
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:05,560
I hope you will look after her.

163
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:08,960
I understand.

164
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:15,000
More than ten years have flown by.

165
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,880
Back then, Your Majesty

166
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,960
wasn't even as tall as Wan Ning is now.

167
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,040
In those days,

168
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:22,160
it was me

169
00:10:22,160 --> 00:10:23,680
who personally carried Your Majesty

170
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:25,280
out of the dog kennel.

171
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,880
Bark like a dog and you'll get food.

172
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,120
No barking, no food.

173
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:34,360
No barking, no food.

174
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,720
Hurry and bark.

175
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:43,400
Duke Zhen saved my life.

176
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,880
I have never forgotten it.

177
00:10:47,880 --> 00:10:50,600
I only hope that Your Majesty and I

178
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,400
will always remain one family.

179
00:11:09,700 --> 00:11:12,740
(Jiang Wanning, Fourth Young Lady
of the Duke's Manor)

180
00:11:17,220 --> 00:11:20,060
(Yuehui Pavilion)

181
00:11:29,540 --> 00:11:30,800
Miss, why don't you rest a bit?

182
00:11:30,800 --> 00:11:31,840
Leave the planting to me.

183
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:33,120
It's fine.

184
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,280
Let's work faster

185
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:37,320
and finish before dark.

186
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,400
Sister.

187
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:45,680
(Whenever Liu Ruyan appears,
nothing good follows.)

188
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,120
Lady Liu.

189
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:53,440
I heard Your Ladyship punished you
by making you plant flowers.

190
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:55,320
In the dead of winter,

191
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,640
how can anything grow?

192
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:59,400
You and I have suffered together before,

193
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:00,760
so I came to help you.

194
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:17,620
(Yuehui Pavilion)

195
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,080
Sister.

196
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,520
How do you use this hoe?

197
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,720
Why don't you...

198
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:30,520
Don't.

199
00:12:36,640 --> 00:12:37,680
Who's there?

200
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:54,020
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

201
00:12:55,740 --> 00:13:00,980
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

202
00:13:02,620 --> 00:13:04,980
♪If we don't meet♪

203
00:13:05,180 --> 00:13:08,420
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

204
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:15,140
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

205
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:21,940
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

206
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:28,620
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

207
00:13:29,140 --> 00:13:35,820
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

208
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:42,700
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

209
00:13:42,940 --> 00:13:48,820
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

210
00:13:49,740 --> 00:13:56,340
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

211
00:13:56,500 --> 00:14:03,180
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

212
00:14:03,460 --> 00:14:09,900
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

